data.name: grdOCS0300.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT MEMB , PK_SEQ , YAKSOK_GUBUN , YAKSOK_GUBUN_NAME , SEQ , HOSP_CODE , MEMB_GUBUN , INPUT_TAB FROM OCS0300 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND MEMB = :f_memb AND INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab ORDER BY SEQ

data.name: grdOCS0301.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.MEMB , A.FKOCS0300_SEQ , A.YAKSOK_CODE , A.YAKSOK_NAME , A.SEQ , A.HOSP_CODE , A.MEMB_GUBUN FROM OCS0301 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MEMB = :f_memb AND A.FKOCS0300_SEQ = :f_fkocs0300_seq ORDER BY A.SEQ

data.name: cboDoctorGwa.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '%', '共通' FROM SYS.DUAL UNION ALL SELECT A.DOCTOR_GWA, B.GWA_NAME FROM BAS0272 A , BAS0260 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SABUN = :f_user_id AND A.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(X.START_DATE) FROM BAS0272 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND X.SABUN = A.SABUN AND X.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.GWA = A.DOCTOR_GWA AND B.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(Z.START_DATE) FROM BAS0260 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND Z.BUSEO_CODE = B.BUSEO_CODE AND Z.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ORDER BY 1

data.name: fwkUser.InputSQL
data.value: SELECT 'ADMIN', '病院共通', 1 FROM SYS.DUAL WHERE :f_query_mode = '0' UNION ALL SELECT A.GWA, A.GWA_NAME, 2 FROM BAS0260 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND :f_query_mode = '0' AND A.GWA IS NOT NULL AND A.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(Z.START_DATE) FROM BAS0260 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.BUSEO_CODE = A.BUSEO_CODE AND Z.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) AND A.GWA_NAME LIKE :f_find1 || '%' UNION ALL SELECT A.USER_ID, B.USER_NM, 3 FROM ADM3200 A, ADM3211 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.USER_ID = A.USER_ID AND B.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(X.START_DATE) FROM ADM3211 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND X.USER_ID = B.USER_ID AND X.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) AND B.USER_NM LIKE :f_find1 || '%' ORDER BY 3, 1
